       "AIMessage(content='In the quiet dawn, the sky awakes,\\nA palette brushed with softest hues,\\nThe sun, a golden artist, gently strokes,\\nA masterpiece of light, where shadows lose.\\n\\nMountains stand as timeless sentinels,\\nTheir peaks kissed by morning mist,\\nForests whisper ancient tales,\\nIn every leaf, a secret exists.\\n\\nRivers dance with liquid grace,\\nTheir silver threads through valleys flow,\\nEach ripple tells a story vast,\\nOf journeys long, and places to go.\\n\\nFields of flowers, vibrant and wild,\\nIn colors bold, they bloom and sway,\\nA symphony of life, a fragrant child,\\nOf earth and sky, in gentle play.\\n\\nThe ocean’s breath, a lullaby,\\nIts waves a rhythmic, endless song,\\nA realm of blue, where secrets lie,\\nBeneath the surface, where wonders throng.\\n\\nBirds take flight, in arcs of grace,\\nTheir songs a melody, pure and free,\\nNature’s beauty, a boundless space,\\nWhere all who wander, find peace.', additional_kwargs={}, response_metadata={'ResponseMetadata': {'RequestId': '72e3df98-a7af-4637-a0e0-ef9b89b5e71c', 'HTTPStatusCode': 200, 'HTTPHeaders': {'date': 'Tue, 14 Jul 2026 06:52:40 GMT', 'content-type': 'application/json', 'content-length': '1115', 'connection': 'keep-alive', 'x-amzn-requestid': '72e3df98-a7af-4637-a0e0-ef9b89b5e71c'}, 'RetryAttempts': 0}, 'stopReason': 'end_turn', 'metrics': {'latencyMs': [1723]}, 'model_provider': 'bedrock_converse', 'model_name': 'amazon.nova-lite-v1:0'}, id='lc_run--019f5f66-2077-7cc0-a8b8-9758b0b41a40-0', tool_calls=[], invalid_tool_calls=[], usage_metadata={'input_tokens': 9, 'output_tokens': 207, 'total_tokens': 216, 'input_token_details': {'cache_creation': 0, 'cache_read': 0}})"
